snippet.title: Breaking the Bank
snippet.description:
This is the start of Henry Stickmin's escapades. I made this back in 2008. I just recently got a newer version of flash and now I can export my flash animations into video. Edited this one a bit to be able to put it on YouTube.

Check out more animations and games from me at puffballsunited.newgrounds.com.
